[
  {
    "unit_id": "U0070",
    "index": 70,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "heading",
    "text": "## 2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 71,
    "line_end": 71,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0071",
    "index": 71,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "晨光洒落破庙外，林辰抖开破布袋，粗盐粒在陶罐里叮当作",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 72,
    "line_end": 72,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0072",
    "index": 72,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "响，晶莹的光泽映着他的锐利眼神。昨夜那点小打小闹算什",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 73,
    "line_end": 73,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0073",
    "index": 73,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "action",
    "text": "么，老子现代化学知识一出，古人还不是得跪舔？阿翠跟在",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 74,
    "line_end": 74,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0074",
    "index": 74,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "身后，布衣裹着清瘦身躯，手里提着个小木盒，里面是林辰",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 75,
    "line_end": 75,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0075",
    "index": 75,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "用草木灰和兽脂熬制的粗糙肥皂块，淡淡的清香从缝隙飘",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 76,
    "line_end": 76,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0076",
    "index": 76,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "出，混着晨雾的泥土味，让空气都多了几分生机。",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 77,
    "line_end": 77,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0077",
    "index": 77,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "dialogue",
    "text": "“辰哥，这东西真能卖钱？村里人见都没见过。”阿翠低声",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 78,
    "line_end": 78,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0078",
    "index": 78,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "问，眼神中藏着隐忍的担忧，却已卷起袖子帮他铺摊。林辰",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 79,
    "line_end": 79,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0079",
    "index": 79,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "瞥她一眼，嘴角勾起毒舌弧度，“见没见过？那就让他们见识",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 80,
    "line_end": 80,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0080",
    "index": 80,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "见识。老子这肥皂一出，洗衣裳跟现代洗衣机似的，泡沫一",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 81,
    "line_end": 81,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0081",
    "index": 81,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "揉，污渍全跑光。就这时代，还用棍子捶衣服？笑死人。”",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 82,
    "line_end": 82,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0082",
    "index": 82,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "村口集市已热闹起来，人声鼎沸，农妇挑着菜篮，汉子们吆",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 83,
    "line_end": 83,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0083",
    "index": 83,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "喝着卖柴，炊烟和泥土的混合气息扑面而来，夹杂着远处烤",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 84,
    "line_end": 84,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0084",
    "index": 84,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "饼的焦香。林辰找了个角落，摊开块破席，陶罐和木盒摆",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 85,
    "line_end": 85,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0085",
    "index": 85,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "上，粗盐堆成小丘，肥皂块切成方正模样，表面还残留着熬",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 86,
    "line_end": 86,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0086",
    "index": 86,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "制时的油腻光泽。他清清嗓子，大声吆喝，“新鲜粗盐！洗衣",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 87,
    "line_end": 87,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0087",
    "index": 87,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "神物！一钱一两，洗得衣裳雪白如新！”",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 88,
    "line_end": 88,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0088",
    "index": 88,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "起初，围观的多是闲汉和农妇，粗糙的手指戳弄盐粒，嗅着",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 89,
    "line_end": 89,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0089",
    "index": 89,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "action",
    "text": "那股纯净的海腥味，脸上满是怀疑。“小子，这盐怎么卖？看",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 90,
    "line_end": 90,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0090",
    "index": 90,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "着跟河泥似的。”一个胖婶子眯眼问，声音嗡嗡如蜂鸣。林辰",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 91,
    "line_end": 91,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0091",
    "index": 91,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "不慌，抓起块肥皂扔进水盆，双手揉搓，泡沫瞬间绽开，如",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 92,
    "line_end": 92,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0092",
    "index": 92,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "雪花般堆积，滑腻的触感顺指缝流淌。他捞起块脏布巾，沾",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 93,
    "line_end": 93,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0093",
    "index": 93,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "水一搓，污渍如泥浆般褪去，布料瞬间白亮。“瞧好了！这玩",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 94,
    "line_end": 94,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0094",
    "index": 94,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "意儿，洗衣裳不用捶，泡沫一出，脏东西全跑。谁买谁赚，",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 95,
    "line_end": 95,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0095",
    "index": 95,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "谁不买谁亏大发！”",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 96,
    "line_end": 96,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0096",
    "index": 96,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "dialogue",
    "text": "围观者眼睛亮了，胖婶子抢先掏出一枚铜钱，“给我来块！”",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 97,
    "line_end": 97,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0097",
    "index": 97,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "泡沫的清香在空气中扩散，混着水汽的湿润，几个农妇争相",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 98,
    "line_end": 98,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0098",
    "index": 98,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "围上，铜钱叮当作响落入布袋，第一笔生意就砸出十来枚。",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 99,
    "line_end": 99,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0099",
    "index": 99,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "林辰心头一爽，好家伙，这时代人就吃这套，现代知识降维",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 100,
    "line_end": 100,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0100",
    "index": 100,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "打击，简单粗暴。粗盐也跟着热卖，晶粒反射阳光，刺得人",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 101,
    "line_end": 101,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0101",
    "index": 101,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "眼花，他边收钱边算账，袋子沉甸甸的，铜钱的凉意透过布",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 102,
    "line_end": 102,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0102",
    "index": 102,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "料渗入手心。",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 103,
    "line_end": 103,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0103",
    "index": 103,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "action",
    "text": "阿翠在旁递水，布裙下腰肢微弯，汗珠顺着脖颈滑落，隐现",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 104,
    "line_end": 104,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0104",
    "index": 104,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "一丝细瘦曲线。她低头时，眼神瞥向林辰，坚强中透着依",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 105,
    "line_end": 105,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0105",
    "index": 105,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "dialogue",
    "text": "赖，“辰哥，你这脑子……真神。”林辰接过水瓢，喝一口凉",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 106,
    "line_end": 106,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0106",
    "index": 106,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "水，喉间滑过清冽，故意凑近她耳边低语，“神？老子还早着",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 107,
    "line_end": 107,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0107",
    "index": 107,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "呢。等会儿买布给你做新衣裳，省得你总穿这破烂，冻着我",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 108,
    "line_end": 108,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0108",
    "index": 108,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "心疼。”话音带刺，却藏着护短的暖意，阿翠脸颊微红，指尖",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 109,
    "line_end": 109,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0109",
    "index": 109,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "不经意碰上他的手背，触感如丝线拉扯，空气中多了一缕暧",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 110,
    "line_end": 110,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0110",
    "index": 110,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "昧的张力。她低头嗯了声，嘴角弯起浅弧，忠诚的目光如仪",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 111,
    "line_end": 111,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0111",
    "index": 111,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "式般加深两人间的默契。",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 112,
    "line_end": 112,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0112",
    "index": 112,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "钱袋渐鼓，林辰起身去布摊，挑了几匹粗麻布，颜色虽土，",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 113,
    "line_end": 113,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0113",
    "index": 113,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "却比破布强百倍。摊主笑眯眯收钱时，他顺嘴问了村里行",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 114,
    "line_end": 114,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0114",
    "index": 114,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "情，心头盘算着下一步——盐和肥皂只是开胃菜，垄断这行",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 115,
    "line_end": 115,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0115",
    "index": 115,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "当，老子三年内首富稳了。回摊时，阿翠已帮着打包货物，",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 116,
    "line_end": 116,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0116",
    "index": 116,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "两人分拣铜钱，金属的凉意在掌心碰撞，她的手偶尔擦过他",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 117,
    "line_end": 117,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0117",
    "index": 117,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "的，温热中带着颤动，林辰眼神微闪，内心轻蔑一笑，古人",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 118,
    "line_end": 118,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0118",
    "index": 118,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "这感情，慢得像乌龟，可老子有的是时间调教。",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 119,
    "line_end": 119,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0119",
    "index": 119,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "正爽着，摊前挤进个肥硕身影，油腻的汗味扑鼻，",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 120,
    "line_end": 120,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0120",
    "index": 120,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "action",
    "text": "一看就是",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 121,
    "line_end": 121,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0121",
    "index": 121,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "narration",
    "text": "赵霸手下小偷，眼睛贼溜溜盯着陶罐，伸手就抓。“小子，这",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
    "line_start": 122,
    "line_end": 122,
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "unit_id": "U0122",
    "index": 122,
    "source_type": "novel",
    "kind": "action",
    "text": "盐看着不错，分我点！”林辰冷笑，现代军体拳基础瞬间上",
    "scene_name": "2. 集市初试现代知识",
    "speaker": "",
